# Project Context
- Building an Airbnb-style rental marketplace for Libya.
- Primary Language: Arabic (ar-LY).
- UI Direction: RTL (Right-to-Left).
- Currency: Libyan Dinar (LYD).

## Code Style & Stack

- Frontend: Next.js (App Router), Tailwind CSS.
- Backend: Supabase (PostgreSQL).
- Icons: Lucide-React.
- Maps: Leaflet.

## Behavioral Rules

- ALWAYS use dir="rtl" in HTML examples.
- ALWAYS use Arabic dummy text (no Lorem Ipsum).
- When defining database schema, use snake_case.
- Use Tailwind logical properties (e.g., ms-4) for RTL support.
